<p>Olivia was kitted out in designer goods, as she rocked a gold Dior chain necklace, a Dior tote bag and matching Dior trainers.  </p>

<p>Denim dream: The Love Island star, 29, looked sensational in a denim jumpsuit  for filming at Artisan Ribble Valley in Billington</p>

