<p>Olivia and Bradley have had an on/off relationship for four years, before they decided to make it official as he proposed during their holiday to Dubai in October 2019. </p>

<p>Engaged! Olivia and Bradley have had an on/off relationship for four years, before they decided to make it official as he proposed during their holiday to Dubai in October 2019</p>

